{"tid":1597880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果《自由之夏》精裝版特刊被搶購一空　再加印6萬本明發售","createTime":"2019-09-27T07:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T11:38:20.000Z","uid":6497,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2127315b6baa69fe66ef3d3daad8a3447ca634bc","tid":1597880,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190927/large/1569565330_6f14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190927%2Flarge%2F1569565330_6f14.jpg&h=3bf6bf51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》今日推出逆權運動100天特刋《自由之夏》粉紙精裝本，讀者反應熱烈，很多地區幾乎售清，現加印六萬本，明天推出，每本仍售10元，扣除成本收益捐6.12人道支援基金。<br />\n香港人，加油！<br />\n<br />\n9.28五周年集會<br />\n日期：9月28日（星期六）<br />\n時間：晚上7時至9時<br />\n地點：添馬公園<br />\n註︰已獲不反對通知書<br />\n主辦︰民間人權陣線<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n10.1國殤遊行<br />\n日期：10月1日（星期二）<br />\n時間：下午2時<br />\n地點：維園集合起步往遮打道<br />\n註︰不反對通知書申請中<br />\n主辦︰民間人權陣線<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n【撐學生】<br />\n召集有心人 撐學生全年睇《蘋果》<br />\n立即按此<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n百日特刊記載香港人逆權之路<br />\n《逆權百日》<br />\n<br />\n《自由之夏》<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n《囚牢之疆》 專頁<br />\n揭開集中營邪惡面紗<br />\n今日新疆 明日香港"},{"pid":"0395cc4ee47c8fe28c720f42ceb79cf735fc740e","tid":1597880,"uid":69933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:01:42.000Z","msg":"留俾我呀你班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56604269405cc0e59130b665f4f75cd11d52fad2","tid":1597880,"uid":270820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:02:05.000Z","msg":"我北角行到炮台山都無啊<br />\n俾福建人買曬？"},{"pid":"b36ba18f3c34f14e1acc540191ab716ed57f2f91","tid":1597880,"uid":12181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rE8uX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi